{"tid":1824951,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"社會上有班人，成世人職業上游走保險地產傳銷","createTime":"2020-01-15T01:19:16.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-15T12:14:07.000Z","uid":40470,"like":50,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"efc224ff976a563666315954fddaabaddba2cfbd","tid":1824951,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T01:19:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有乜共通點？<br />\n<br />\n1. 學歷要求低<br />\n<br />\n2. 自稱專業人士<br />\n<br />\n3. 口裡成日講正能量，堅持<br />\n<br />\n4. 行業上位者搵大錢，下位者扮搵大錢：有錢同窮既比例 1:25<br />\n<br />\n5. 著西裝<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n6. 一般不受普遍社會尊重<br />\n<br />\n呢班人做唔掂保險，就走去做地產。做唔掂地產，就做傳銷。做唔掂傳銷，就走返去做保險<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n點解？<br />\n<br />\n因為佢地真係好鐘意著西裝扮返工<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n佢地Hea下hea下就中年，一事無成<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9cb94420d3ee9a1036972634ca4ba0b38818fba9","tid":1824951,"uid":40470,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T01:20:58.000Z","msg":"佢地當中會有小數突然覺醒<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n然後走去做倫敦金<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n可能100個當中有個會上位發達<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd863842ce24ca07d10dab13357e852685a3d8ce","tid":1824951,"uid":40470,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T01:27:44.000Z","msg":"點解會跌入呢個無間循環？<br />\n<br />\n因為唔肯面對現實<br />\n<br />\n學歷低，又要學年分專業人士要著西裝返工<br />\n<br />\n一開始搵唔到正常工<br />\n<br />\n呢d咁既行業，只要正常人就請<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f22096134233ff5b4252579b62d7384957fc8065","tid":1824951,"uid":105863,"like":4,"disli